{"tid":2328923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"李偲嫣猝死︱屢違限聚零告票 除罩飛沫近距噴議員 事主致悼：來生再做中國人","createTime":"2020-12-17T01:14:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T08:22:52.000Z","uid":130626,"like":739,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"f39eb0a87d8f4085f77a60aa8cc1031f7d75e7a5","tid":2328923,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:14:56.000Z","msg":"死忠藍絲、盲撐梁振英的正義聯盟創辦人李偲嫣，昨（16日）寓所暈倒，送院1小時猝死，並驗出武肺病毒，終年56歲。李偲嫣是否中武肺而死，仍待確定，但疫情期間，卻多次忽視防疫規定，雖未被警察票控，但足見其衞生意識薄弱。例如李偲嫣帶頭違反限聚令，率眾集結；向警務處處長鄧炳強獻花時，為求向其一展容顏，竟拉低口罩；與政見不同的區議員爭吵時，又拉低口罩，或令飛沫近距噴向對方面部。當日受害的區議員李志宏在Facebook致悼，祝李偲嫣「來生再做中國人」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/JSB25NIE5NFR7PUPFKVN3HXFKQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FJSB25NIE5NFR7PUPFKVN3HXFKQ%2F&d=c%2B6PkbrQ5MzYtHY5m9tE10B1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=069ef0e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FJSB25NIE5NFR7PUPFKVN3HXFKQ%2F&h=f12dbfea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/JSB25NIE5NFR7PUPFKVN3HXFKQ/</a>"},{"pid":"733b9c016d5984f37c333ee37f6cc53590d675ac","tid":2328923,"uid":295230,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:17:07.000Z","msg":"RAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc055266d19d40d19e1b061ecf6022f97b3008b8","tid":2328923,"uid":79793,"like":637,"dislike":1,"score":636,"citedBy":16,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:17:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">祝李偲嫣「來生再做中國人」<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3663a72742b33438c8f6edab7828cf68bf4734c2","tid":2328923,"uid":28590,"like":138,"dislike":0,"score":138,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T01:18:50.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁<br />\n輪迴再做中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkg